Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.62,0:00:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you know
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.34,0:00:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,that cocks can be sucked like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.98,0:00:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought of doing something to make your feel good
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.76,0:00:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,so I did some studying.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.20,0:00:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.89,0:00:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to move, okay Mishiro-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.30,0:01:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you, Mishiro-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.20,0:01:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.84,0:01:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Mishiro-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.32,0:02:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.47,0:02:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Those were the first words that she said to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.41,0:02:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Fleetingly short,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.12,0:02:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,but it was the start of the most joyful part of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.49,0:03:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,As I lay on that hard bed, I understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.03,0:03:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That the next time I woke up,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.72,0:03:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I would learn of the fact that I was "eaten".
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.31,0:03:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.66,0:03:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,If I had arrived sooner, I could have\Nsaved at least half of your soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.43,0:03:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Who, am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.77,0:03:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So your memories are...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.39,0:03:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems that the cause of your memory loss,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.33,0:03:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,is you yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.29,0:03:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Kazamidori.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.59,0:03:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You are Mishiro-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.46,0:03:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Your soul, which was taken from you, is not yet lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.20,0:03:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll bring back the memories of your soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.66,0:04:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Because someday "it" will once again appear before you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.51,0:04:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,She then kept her promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.30,0:04:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Since then, she was always by my side,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.84,0:04:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,and taught me lots of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.75,0:04:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,She was my everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.93,0:04:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,She filled the void made by my lost soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.95,0:04:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a tranquil and peaceful time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.53,0:04:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.97,0:04:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The Aragami that once again appeared,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.12,0:04:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,took her life as she tried to protect me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.19,0:04:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Tsuina Mishiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.46,0:04:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.70,0:04:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It just can't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.09,0:04:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,She just can't be her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.73,0:04:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,\NShe's gone already.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.92,0:04:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Died right before my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.04,0:05:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not familiar with the current\Nlessons at the moment, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.79,0:05:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall I lend you my notes then?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.85,0:05:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Its boring to just space out by yourself, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.59,0:05:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall I introduce you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.91,0:05:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We could start with a few guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.68,0:05:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll show you around the school.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.51,0:05:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll need it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.50,0:05:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Considering your school life here from how on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.23,0:05:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you spacing out?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.94,0:05:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Remembered something bad from before?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.53,0:05:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's normal for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.63,0:05:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be that he was being bullied before he moved here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.37,0:05:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,My, how scandalous!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.84,0:05:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.92,0:05:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's just put it that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.27,0:05:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Why aren't you answering me directly?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.46,0:05:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I got smacked in the face as I was walking in the streets.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.08,0:05:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,This town isn't that violent, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.33,0:06:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go with you next time when I don't have club activities.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.75,0:06:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.13,0:06:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.48,0:06:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.52,0:06:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you haven't even asked me a question or two yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.29,0:06:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Not even my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.60,0:06:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You're absolutely not uninterested in me, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.17,0:06:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, at least try to deny the last part!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.80,0:06:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You're Yuki, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.58,0:06:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.17,0:06:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right, I'm Yuigahama Yuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.35,0:06:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Still need something from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.86,0:06:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Just so you know, that attitude won't work on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.40,0:06:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Something just needs to happen between you and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.90,0:06:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Or else this fuzzy feeling in my heart won't go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.04,0:06:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.83,0:06:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't mean that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.90,0:06:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't mean I'd like a kiss or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.36,0:06:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't mean it in a lewd way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.23,0:06:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.62,0:07:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you feel anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.73,0:07:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.95,0:07:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine then! Geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.37,0:07:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What are those?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.88,0:07:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Monsters?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.70,0:07:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You can see them?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.37,0:07:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,But they're plainly there...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.55,0:07:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.49,0:07:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,She can see a Kotowari?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.17,0:08:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,No way, that's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.88,0:08:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The Reishin!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.02,0:08:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,A Kotowari is a fragment of one's soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.13,0:08:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Normally, it's only seen by the life\Nform or entity that it came from,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.43,0:08:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,but there are exceptions, such as those with damaged souls
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.58,0:08:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and those who are roughly connected\Nto them in some way such as myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.95,0:08:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.38,0:08:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know what a Kotowari is?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.09,0:08:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.08,0:08:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that what those monsters are called?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.03,0:08:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You thought it was a monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.22,0:08:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,My family is a Shinto household,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.16,0:08:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,maybe that's why I can see those monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.36,0:08:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry Mishiro-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.39,0:08:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,See you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.90,0:09:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,See you then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.23,0:09:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Wretched one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.82,0:09:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you come to this place?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.73,0:09:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.72,0:09:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Drive him out!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.47,0:09:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.02,0:09:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I have something to ask of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.93,0:09:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandma!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.44,0:09:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The Reishin
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.71,0:09:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,was something that was passed down within Yuki's family.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.74,0:09:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It was actually her aunt, the one that\Ntook care of her, who inherited it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.55,0:09:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Though, there's nothing much that\Nshe remembers about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.10,0:09:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That was how Yuki explained it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.55,0:09:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,When I simply spoke the name of Kazamidori...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.22,0:09:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So this place is connected to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.83,0:09:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.83,0:09:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.86,0:09:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I just bade goodbye to her earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.50,0:09:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Kazamidori-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.01,0:09:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Kazamidori-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.20,0:09:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,She can't be alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.43,0:10:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,She's already dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.42,0:10:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw it with my very own eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.48,0:10:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.06,0:10:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.30,0:10:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't rob me of this power!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.36,0:10:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the only thing that I have!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.27,0:10:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything will then be lost to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.42,0:10:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I need this power, and I need to retrieve something back!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.87,0:10:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't do that mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.98,0:10:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,This method won't help you reach out to your wife and kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.36,0:10:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki was able to touch his heart using the Reishin.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.14,0:10:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know exactly what she saw though.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.60,0:10:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.76,0:10:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill them all!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.17,0:11:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that was quite a risk.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.11,0:11:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.18,0:11:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.54,0:11:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What a nice night sky we have here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.72,0:11:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a report made from your house that\Nyou were being assaulted by some hoodlum.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.92,0:11:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you alright, Yuki-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.70,0:11:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You're from Grandma's...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.17,0:11:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Please leave the remaining task to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.43,0:11:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That person, simply wanted to be accepted.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.28,0:11:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But no one ever noticed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.41,0:11:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.77,0:11:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand that it was wrong of him to have\Ndone that bad thing in the first place, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.51,0:11:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The one who took over that was Grandma, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.52,0:12:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Mishiro-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.33,0:12:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's a Kotowari!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.45,0:12:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.51,0:12:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsuina Mishiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.95,0:12:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It is your fault that I died.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.81,0:12:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I was devoured by the abomination that you held.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.43,0:12:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You should have been the one who died.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.50,0:12:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.39,0:12:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.35,0:13:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you capable of doing such a terrible thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.78,0:13:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Driving down Mishiro-kun like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.85,0:13:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What were you thinking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.59,0:13:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Answer me, Grandma!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.57,0:13:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.40,0:13:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Mishiro-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.39,0:13:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Kotowari ~The spilled fragments of the heart~
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.42,0:13:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I feel like meddling between you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.45,0:13:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I was wondering how far the two of you had progress
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.24,0:13:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,since you're always together.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.67,0:13:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, try to put a plug on that youth of yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.80,0:13:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be that we made Kiyomi worried?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.95,0:13:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So you consult Kiyomi on a variety of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.53,0:13:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I talk about everything with her,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.72,0:13:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and I thought I might be bothering you enough already.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.50,0:13:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.49,0:14:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I still see those dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.83,0:14:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's completely pitch black.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.50,0:14:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I can hear children crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.33,0:14:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.01,0:14:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No need to force yourself to remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.41,0:14:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you can be by my side forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.61,0:14:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, now I feel better.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.28,0:14:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't do anything though.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.06,0:14:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel better when I am with you and talking about things.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.40,0:14:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,So, please stay by my side from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.11,0:14:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That way I will feel a lot better.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.02,0:14:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.53,0:15:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,How did she die?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.03,0:15:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,She was...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.07,0:15:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Aunty was...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.94,0:15:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.52,0:15:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,She protected you, and allowed you meet\NYuki because of her prudence, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.17,0:15:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The fact that both you and Yuki are here now,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.83,0:15:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,is already considered a miracle.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.98,0:15:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,She was incapable of seeing Kotowari before you came.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.76,0:15:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,However Yuki, you can see her now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.90,0:15:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You were also lighted with the treatment\Nthat was given to him by her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.00,0:15:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,She gave up her life in order to compensate\Nfor the damage done to your soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.44,0:16:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So inside of me, part of Kazamidori-san's soul is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.11,0:16:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, she wasn't able to fight at her\Nfull strength because of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.92,0:16:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki also has a fragment of her soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.33,0:16:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That heart of yours was transplanted\Nto you when you were young.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.71,0:16:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It was hers.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.97,0:16:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The day when Mishiro came to the household,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.48,0:16:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt a certain throb in my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.15,0:16:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,So, if part of aunty's feelings remained in this heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.61,0:16:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.28,0:16:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You must have realized it already.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.99,0:16:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You are the one who killed her!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.73,0:16:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason why that left hand still moves
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.96,0:16:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,is because your damaged soul is still somewhere within you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.30,0:16:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,A Kotowari is a fragment of a disintegrated soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.20,0:16:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Then that means...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.87,0:16:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,A fragment of Mishiro-kun's soul
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.14,0:16:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,is still living inside the Aragami?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.60,0:16:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.55,0:17:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,A Kotowari cannot be seen except by the one\Nwho owns the soul where it came from!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.77,0:17:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Where do you think the Aragami came from?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.68,0:17:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That would be... my own Kotowari.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.18,0:17:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That was me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.88,0:17:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You're feeling awkward towards Yuki at the moment, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.62,0:17:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,She really feels down.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.25,0:17:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But you two did not have an argument, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.32,0:17:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,She's really worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.90,0:17:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You're to meet her at four in the afternoon,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.29,0:17:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,so you'd better take a bath and prepare.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.26,0:18:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't forgive myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.20,0:18:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,For driving Kazamidori-san to her death...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.58,0:18:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Both of us hold parts of Aunty's soul, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.03,0:18:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.78,0:18:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.41,0:18:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You say you can't forgive yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.68,0:18:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,and I also feel the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.02,0:18:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason why I can feel joy at this moment
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.05,0:18:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,is all because of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.89,0:19:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I can only think of being one with you right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.98,0:20:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.95,0:20:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Mishiro-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.18,0:20:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.53,0:20:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you come out?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.44,0:20:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You are me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.55,0:20:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you kill...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.54,0:20:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you kill her?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.57,0:20:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You are supposed to be me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.11,0:20:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Won't any of my prayers be answered?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.81,0:20:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I don't need you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.31,0:21:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Be gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.36,0:21:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.07,0:21:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you prepared to kill that Kotowari
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.78,0:21:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,at the cost of losing your arm?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.04,0:21:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.78,0:21:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,These are letters passed on to me by her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.95,0:21:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Your past is written there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.93,0:21:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I was I finally able to establish contact with\Nthe boy that is tainted by his Kotowari.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.62,0:21:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,He was the grandchild of an old lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.65,0:21:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,He was taken in after the unfortunate death of his parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.68,0:21:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The old lady carried out abortion for a living.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.78,0:21:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Her hands did not waver as she did her job.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.80,0:22:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,She contemplated on it for while,\Nbut in the end he took the boy in.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.61,0:22:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Then thought of using the small hands of the boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.67,0:22:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,She taught him the techniques\Nthat were passed down to her,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.34,0:22:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,in order to keep the household.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.73,0:22:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I now know the identity of the boy's Kotowari.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.88,0:22:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the consciousness of his sins.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.33,0:22:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,He considered the countless infants\Nthat passed through his hands,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.88,0:22:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,as souls that he himself had murdered.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.10,0:22:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,He touched those souls, and felt\Nthe stain of death within them.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.51,0:22:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I implored the old lady to stop what they were doing,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.06,0:22:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,but the old lady simply would not listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.40,0:22:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I had yet to tell the worst thing that could come out of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.74,0:22:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The boy continued to be pained by it
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.69,0:22:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,and by attempting to pull out the fragment\Nof his soul that contained those memories
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.87,0:22:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,a frightening Kotowari came into existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.92,0:22:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That Kotowari is still alive as I speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.09,0:23:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I must find the Aragami's whereabouts
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.30,0:23:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and erase his sins.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.48,0:23:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That is what my heart wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.81,0:23:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do, Kazamidori-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.60,0:23:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Kazamidori-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.43,0:23:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.91,0:23:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.80,0:23:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry now then.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.69,0:23:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Kazamidori-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.60,0:23:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Save this girl, quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.15,0:23:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Kazamidori-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.28,0:24:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.72,0:24:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't fight it using your hatred!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.20,0:24:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Trust the words of Aunty.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.88,0:24:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.94,0:24:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That thing is a fragment of one's soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.29,0:24:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the only one who can accept it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.47,0:24:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Accept it?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.58,0:24:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it protecting something?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.19,0:25:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason why Aunty's Kotowari was attacked by it
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.97,0:25:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,was because she attacked its belly.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.88,0:25:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,She wanted to get me back.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.31,0:25:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,A weak point.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.78,0:25:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll try to restrain it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.49,0:25:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Target the belly, understood Mishiro-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.23,0:25:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you dare hurt Yuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.98,0:25:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't snatch anything from me anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.08,0:25:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are...!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.67,0:25:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, I beg of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.41,0:25:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Mishiro-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.00,0:25:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I beg of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.21,0:25:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Many lives were lost by my own hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.87,0:25:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care what happens to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.21,0:25:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why, please...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.95,0:25:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Remain with me, the sensation within my hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.82,0:25:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,May all these poor souls,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.28,0:26:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,be lifted to where my mother is!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.08,0:26:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You were protecting it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.06,0:26:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The lives of all those unborn children,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.41,0:26:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,and the tender heart of the man I love the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.38,0:26:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So you went out to return those.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.25,0:26:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You will live, to continue carrying those sins.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.08,0:26:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Because your sins, are my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.09,0:26:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.38,0:26:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.61,0:26:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop that!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.97,0:27:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Mishiro-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.34,0:27:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Mishiro-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.83,0:27:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to cum.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.78,0:28:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So you can also act spoiled sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.89,0:28:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You're really helpless, Mishiro-kun.